Fields are:
-----------
pmid 
span_id
section
gene
mesh_id
mesh_tree

All fields are searchable.

section:category 
----------------
where category has values:

title
references
abstract
abbreviations
conclusions
results,
introduction
methods
footnotes
acknowledgments
appendix
future
cases
grants
main    (main text)
nc  (not categorized)

gene:name
---------
where name is the gene name from the Trec questions with no space
starting with a 'ss', 'sw', 'ws' or 'ww'.

First prefix letter: strong (s) or Weak (w) in the QUERY.
Second prefix letter: strong (s) or Weak (w) in the DOCUMENT.

Example query:
--------------
pmid:14610078 gene:ssp53 "Western analyses using antibodies"

Search the article with pmid 14610078 for genes p53 and containing the phrase 
"Western analyses using antibodies".

All Lucene operators:
---------------------
http://lucene.apache.org/java/docs/queryparsersyntax.html
